tip.text: The Sweet Trinity is awesome! Give ita try!
Their sushis are superb! Great quality. Though pricey.
Good service & no hard selling. Price is cheap as compared to other spas. Try the Asian Fusion Oil Massage for 60mins at only $58! So worth it!
Saturday dinner buffet is seafood bbq. Great service from staff with quality food. Love this place!

tip.text: Prata is nice & not oily. Teh tarik is oomph!

Popiah skin with ice cream & peanut. This is simple but super yummy! A must to try in Jiufen.
Chendol here is awesome! Not to be missed.
Best to sit outside where there's natural cool air for chillaxing. Nice place for brunch.
Tunisian is super good! A must-try.
